{"id":46,"parent_id":1,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":46,"title":"Genesis 45","subtitle":"","short_title":"Gen.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/45","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 45"],[".studySummary",["i","Joseph makes himself known to his brothers—They rejoice together—Pharaoh invites Jacob and his family to dwell in Egypt and eat the fat of the land."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/45.1","order":"02.02.045.4007"},["b","1"],"Then Joseph could not",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"refrain"],"himself before all them that stood by him; and he",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"cried"],", Cause every man to go out from me. And there stood no man with him, while Joseph made himself known unto his brethren."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/45.2","order":"02.02.045.4008"},["b","2"],"And he wept aloud: and the Egyptians and the house of Pharaoh heard."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/45.3","order":"02.02.045.4009"},["b","3"],"And Joseph said unto his brethren, I",["i","am"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"Joseph"],"; doth my father yet live? And his brethren could not answer him; for they were",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"troubled"],"at his presence."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/45.4","order":"02.02.045.4010"},["b","4"],"And Joseph said unto his brethren, Come near to me, I pray you. And they came near. And he said, I",["i","am"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"Joseph"],"your brother, whom ye sold into Egypt."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/45.5","order":"02.02.045.4011"},["b","5"],"Now therefore be not",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"grieved"],", nor angry with yourselves, that ye sold me hither: for God did",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"send"],"me before you to preserve life."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/45.6","order":"02.02.045.4012"},["b","6"],"For these two years",["i","hath"],"the famine",["i","been"],"in the land: and yet",["i","there are"],"five years, in the which",["i","there shall"],"neither",["i","be"],"earing nor harvest."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/45.7","order":"02.02.045.4013"},["b","7"],"And God sent me before you to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"preserve"],"you a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"posterity"],"in the earth, and to save your lives by a great deliverance."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/45.8","order":"02.02.045.4014"},["b","8"],"So now",["i","it was"],"not you",["i","that"],"sent me hither, but God: and he hath made me a father to Pharaoh, and lord of all his house, and a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"ruler"],"throughout all the land of Egypt."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/45.9","order":"02.02.045.4015"},["b","9"],"Haste ye, and go up to my father, and say unto him, Thus saith thy son Joseph, God hath made me lord of all Egypt: come down unto me, tarry not:"],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/45.10","order":"02.02.045.4016"},["b","10"],"And thou shalt dwell in the land of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"Goshen"],", and thou shalt be near unto me, thou, and thy children, and thy children’s children, and thy flocks, and thy herds, and all that thou hast:"],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/45.11","order":"02.02.045.4017"},["b","11"],"And there will I",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"nourish"],"thee; for yet",["i","there are"],"five years of famine; lest thou, and thy household, and all that thou hast, come to poverty."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/45.12","order":"02.02.045.4018"},["b","12"],"And, behold, your eyes see, and the eyes of my brother Benjamin, that",["i","it is"],"my mouth that speaketh unto you."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/45.13","order":"02.02.045.4019"},["b","13"],"And ye shall tell my father of all my glory in Egypt, and of all that ye have seen; and ye shall haste and bring down my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"father"],"hither."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/45.14","order":"02.02.045.4020"},["b","14"],"And he fell upon his brother Benjamin’s neck, and wept; and Benjamin wept upon his neck."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/45.15","order":"02.02.045.4021"},["b","15"],"Moreover he kissed all his brethren, and wept upon them: and after that his brethren talked with him."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/45.16","order":"02.02.045.4022"},["b","16"],"¶And the fame thereof was heard in Pharaoh’s house, saying, Joseph’s brethren are come: and it",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"pleased"],"Pharaoh well, and his servants."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/45.17","order":"02.02.045.4023"},["b","17"],"And Pharaoh said unto Joseph, Say unto thy brethren, This do ye; lade your beasts, and go, get you unto the land of Canaan;"],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/45.18","order":"02.02.045.4024"},["b","18"],"And take your father and your households, and come unto me: and I will give you the good of the land of Egypt, and ye shall eat the fat of the land."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/45.19","order":"02.02.045.4025"},["b","19"],"Now thou art commanded, this do ye; take you",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"wagons"],"out of the land of Egypt for your little ones, and for your wives, and bring your father, and come."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/45.20","order":"02.02.045.4026"},["b","20"],"Also regard not your stuff; for the good of all the land of Egypt",["i","is"],"yours."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/45.21","order":"02.02.045.4027"},["b","21"],"And the children of Israel did so: and Joseph gave them wagons, according to the commandment of Pharaoh, and gave them provision for the way."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/45.22","order":"02.02.045.4028"},["b","22"],"To all of them he gave each man changes of raiment; but to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"Benjamin"],"he gave three hundred",["i","pieces"],"of silver, and five changes of raiment."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/45.23","order":"02.02.045.4029"},["b","23"],"And to his father he sent after this",["i","manner;"],"ten asses laden with the good things of Egypt, and ten she asses laden with corn and bread and meat for his father by the way."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/45.24","order":"02.02.045.4030"},["b","24"],"So he sent his brethren away, and they departed: and he said unto them, See that ye fall not out by the way."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/45.25","order":"02.02.045.4031"},["b","25"],"¶And they went up out of Egypt, and came into the land of Canaan unto Jacob their father,"],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/45.26","order":"02.02.045.4032"},["b","26"],"And told him, saying, Joseph",["i","is"],"yet alive, and he",["i","is"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"governor"],"over all the land of Egypt. And Jacob’s heart fainted, for he believed them not."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/45.27","order":"02.02.045.4033"},["b","27"],"And they told him all the words of Joseph, which he had said unto them: and when he saw the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_27a"},"wagons"],"which Joseph had sent to carry him, the spirit of Jacob their father",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_27b"},"revived"],":"],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/45.28","order":"02.02.045.4034"},["b","28"],"And Israel said,",["i","It is"],"enough; Joseph my son",["i","is"],"yet alive: I will go and see him before I die."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/45.1a","order":"02.02.045.4035"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/43.30.30-31"},"Gen. 43:30 (30–31)"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/45.1b","order":"02.02.045.4037"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/46.29"},"Gen. 46:29"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/45.3a","order":"02.02.045.4039"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/7.13"},"Acts 7:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/45.3b","order":"02.02.045.4041"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/job/23.15"},"Job 23:15"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/45.4a","order":"02.02.045.4043"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/3.4"},"2 Ne. 3:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/45.5a","order":"02.02.045.4045"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/benevolence"},"TG Benevolence"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/family-love-within"},"Family, Love within"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/45.5b","order":"02.02.045.4047"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/50.20"},"Gen. 50:20"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/105.17"},"Ps. 105:17"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/45.7a","order":"02.02.045.4049"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/esth/4.14"},"Esth. 4:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/3.16"},"2 Ne. 3:16"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/107.42"},"D&C 107:42"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/protection-divine"},"TG Protection, Divine"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/45.7b","order":"02.02.045.4051"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/3.3,5.3-7"},"2 Ne. 3:3, 5 (3–7)"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/45.8a","order":"02.02.045.4053"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/41.43.41-44"},"Gen. 41:43 (41–44)"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/45.10a","order":"02.02.045.4055"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/46.28.28-34"},"Gen. 46:28 (28–34)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/47.1.1,11"},"47:1 (1, 11)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/50.8"},"50:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/45.11a","order":"02.02.045.4057"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/47.12"},"Gen. 47:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/45.13a","order":"02.02.045.4059"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/7.14"},"Acts 7:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/45.16a","order":"02.02.045.4061"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/41.37"},"Gen. 41:37"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/45.19a","order":"02.02.045.4063"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/46.5"},"Gen. 46:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.5"},"D&C 136:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/45.22a","order":"02.02.045.4065"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/43.34"},"Gen. 43:34"],"."],["div",{"id":"26a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/45.26a","order":"02.02.045.4067"},["b","26a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/41.43.41-44"},"Gen. 41:43 (41–44)"],"."],["div",{"id":"27a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/45.27a","order":"02.02.045.4069"},["b","27a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/7.3.3,5"},"Num. 7:3 (3, 5)"],"."],["div",{"id":"27b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/gen/45.27b","order":"02.02.045.4071"},["b","27b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/46.5.3-5"},"Gen. 46:5 (3–5)"],"."]]}
